'''[[lanolin]]'''

# (''uncountable'') A [[greasy]] yellow [[substance]] chemically akin to [[wax]] that is [[secrete]]d from [[wooly]] animals, with a variety of uses from [[rust]] prevention, [[lubrication]] and [[water-proofing]] to [[cosmetics]] and skin [[ointment]]s.

